================================================================================
Attribution — derived from the mpump suite
================================================================================

mspectr is part of the mpump suite of browser-native music instruments and
reuses patterns, code, and conventions from its sibling projects. All siblings
are licensed under AGPL-3.0; derived material remains under the same license.

Sibling projects this work derives from:
  - mpump    — the suite's foundational groovebox and shared conventions
  - mgrains  — granular instrument (service-worker and PWA-shell patterns)
  - mscope   — spectral/visualization tooling
  - mdrone   — drone instrument (PWA manifest and icon conventions)
  - mloop    — looping instrument
  - mpumpit  — the GitHub Pages deploy workflow and AGPL LICENSE template

Derived files and the sibling source they were adapted from:

  Instrument & MIDI
  - src/instrument/keyboard.ts         — Ableton-style QWERTY layout adapted
                                         from mpumpit/src/midi/qwerty.ts
                                         (drum mode removed; melodic only)
  - src/midi/router.ts, parse.ts,
    types.ts                           — router/parse/ownership model adapted
                                         from mpumpit/src/midi/* (added pitch
                                         bend, sustain, single-instrument route)

  Sources
  - src/sources/live.ts, tab.ts,
    file.ts, capabilities.ts           — getUserMedia/getDisplayMedia constraints,
                                         no-audio-track guard, decode/teardown
                                         flow adapted from mscope/src/audio/input/*

  Performance
  - src/performance/macros.ts          — macro link/unlink takeover model adapted
                                         from mgrains/src/audio/macros.ts
  - src/performance/presets.ts         — preset structure + per-preset loudness
                                         trim adapted from mdrone/src/engine/presets.ts

  Persistence
  - src/persistence/*                  — defensive IndexedDB + forward-sanitizing
                                         deserialization adapted from
                                         mgrains/src/storage/presets.ts

  Recording & transport
  - src/recording/wav.ts               — RIFF/PCM encoder adapted from
                                         mloop/src/utils/wav.ts (24-bit added)
  - src/recording/wavRecorder.ts,
    recorder.worklet.ts                — recorder lifecycle adapted from
                                         mloop/src/engine/Recorder.ts
  - src/transport/linkBridge.ts        — Ableton Link bridge client adapted from
                                         mdrone/src/engine/linkBridge.ts

  PWA / build / deploy
  - public/sw.js                       — adapted from mgrains/public/sw.js
  - .github/workflows/deploy.yml       — adapted from the mpumpit/mgrains
                                         GitHub Pages workflow
  - .github/workflows/ci.yml           — adapted from the suite CI workflow
  - public/manifest.webmanifest        — conventions from mdrone manifest
  - LICENSE                            — AGPL-3.0 text from the mpumpit LICENSE

  Original work (no sibling derivation)
  - src/audio/dsp/* (FFT, windows, STFT, overlap-add, phase, spectral frame,
    and all spectral operations: morph, shift, formant, blur, tilt, gate,
    harmonize, freeze, reverb, limiter), src/audio/SpectralEngine.ts, the
    spectral AudioWorklet, contracts, and the spectral visualization are
    original to mspectr.

